@page
@model PrivacyModel
@{
    Layout = "_Header";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}


<div class="policy-container">
    <div class="policy">
        <h1 class="policy-title">Privacy & Policy</h1>

        <p class="policy-paragraph">
            At <strong>Health Connect</strong>, we are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your data when you use our platform, including online consultations, pharmacy services, health blogs, and more.
        </p>

        <h2 class="policy-subtitle">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="policy-paragraph">
            We collect personal information you voluntarily provide when you register, book an appointment, consult with a doctor, or order medicine. This includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="policy-list">
            <li>✔ Name, Email, Phone Number</li>
            <li>✔ Date of Birth, Gender</li>
            <li>✔ Medical history and health-related data</li>
            <li>✔ Chat and video consultation records (encrypted)</li>
            <li>✔ Payment details (processed securely)</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="policy-subtitle">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="policy-paragraph">We use your data to:</p>
        <ul class="policy-list">
            <li>✔ Provide personalized healthcare services</li>
            <li>✔ Schedule and manage appointments</li>
            <li>✔ Communicate with you about prescriptions, reminders, and updates</li>
            <li>✔ Improve platform performance and user experience</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="policy-subtitle">3. Data Sharing & Security</h2>
        <p class="policy-paragraph">
            We do not sell or rent your data. We may share it only with verified doctors or pharmacy providers to fulfill your requests. All data transfers are encrypted, and your medical records are stored securely.
        </p>

        <h2 class="policy-subtitle">4. Cookies & Tracking</h2>
        <p class="policy-paragraph">
            We use cookies to enhance user experience and analyze website traffic. You can manage cookie preferences in your browser settings.
        </p>

        <h2 class="policy-subtitle">5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="policy-paragraph">
            You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal data at any time. You can also opt out of promotional messages by updating your communication preferences.
        </p>

        <h2 class="policy-subtitle">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="policy-paragraph">
            We may use third-party services for secure payments, video conferencing, or analytics. These providers are contractually obligated to protect your data.
        </p>

        <h2 class="policy-subtitle">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="policy-paragraph">
            Health Connect may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review it regularly. Significant changes will be communicated via email or on the website.
        </p>

        <p class="policy-paragraph">
            For any questions or concerns regarding this policy, please contact our support team at <strong>healthconnect058@gmail.com</strong>.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

